data.enText: to use machines and computers instead of people to do a job or task

data.chText: 整个生产过程已自动化。
data.enText: The entire manufacturing process has been automated.

data.chText: 这家工厂现在是全自动化。
data.enText: The factory is now fully automated .

tr: make automatic or control or operate automatically
example: automate the movement of the robot

value.def: To automate a factory, office, or industrial process means to put in machines which can do the work instead of people.

example.ex: He wanted to use computers to automate the process.
example.tran: 他想通过计算机实现流程的自动化。

example.ex: In the last ten years automation has reduced the work force here by half.
example.tran: 过去的10年里，自动化使这里的工人总数减少了一半。
